msgstr "14 days"

#: templates/policies/returns_policy.html:14
msgid "bez podawania przyczyny."
msgstr "without giving any reason."

#: templates/policies/returns_policy.html:16
msgid ""
"Termin biegnie od dnia, w którym objąłeś towar w posiadanie (lub osoba przez "
"Ciebie wskazana)."
msgstr ""
"The deadline runs from the day on which you (or a person indicated by you) "
"took possession of the goods."

#: templates/policies/returns_policy.html:17
