"w sposób jednoznaczny (np. listownie, e‑mail lub za pomocą formularza na "
"stronie)."
msgstr ""
"To exercise the right of withdrawal, you must inform us of your decision in an "
"unequivocal way (e.g. by post, email or using a form on the site)."

#: templates/policies/returns_policy.html:18
msgid "Możesz skorzystać z"
msgstr "You may use"

#: templates/policies/returns_policy.html:18
msgid "wzoru formularza odstąpienia"
msgstr "the withdrawal form template"

#: templates/policies/returns_policy.html:18
msgid ", ale nie jest to obowiązkowe."
msgstr ", but it is not obligatory."

#: templates/policies/returns_policy.html:22
msgid "⚠️ Ważny wyjątek dla perfum:"
msgstr "⚠️ Important exception for perfumes:"

#: templates/policies/returns_policy.html:22
msgid ""
"Zgodnie z art. 38 ustawy o prawach konsumenta, prawo odstąpienia od umowy"
msgstr "Under Art. 38 of the Consumer Rights Act, the right of withdrawal"

#: templates/policies/returns_policy.html:22
msgid "nie przysługuje"
msgstr "does not apply"

#: templates/policies/returns_policy.html:22
