"nas metody)."
msgstr ""
"Upon withdrawal, you only bear the direct costs of returning the goods (the "
"cost of shipping back to us). We refund you the full amount paid for the "
"product (including basic delivery costs – the cheapest method we offer)."

#: templates/policies/returns_policy.html:28
